        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sections-overview">
    <p class="section-kicker">Destaques do site</p>
    <h2>Por onde começar</h2>
    <div class="grid editorial-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Comece por aqui</h3>
        <p>Guia rápido para escolher sua trilha conforme o perfil e o objetivo de estudo.</p>
        <a href="comece-por-aqui/">Entrar</a>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>IA Forense</h3>
        <p>Ferramentas, método, prompts, verificação e cautelas para uso prático no Direito.</p>
        <a href="ia-forense/">Explorar</a>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Primeiro fluxo de IA em petição</h3>
        <p>Um roteiro inicial para usar IA com método, revisão crítica e controle das fontes.</p>
        <a href="ia-forense/primeiro-fluxo-ia-peticao/">Ler artigo</a>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Vocabulário tecnológico</h3>
        <p>Glossário tecnológico-jurídico para aprender os termos essenciais sem ruído.</p>
        <a href="vocabulario/">Consultar</a>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Biblioteca</h3>
        <p>Vídeos, normas, documentos públicos, referências e materiais recomendados.</p>
        <a href="biblioteca/">Ver curadoria</a>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Reflexão em evidência</h3>
        <p>Ética, regulação, responsabilidade profissional e limites da IA na prática forense.</p>
        <a href="reflexoes/">Abrir reflexões</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-copy {
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .author-line {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 0.72rem 0 0.82rem;
    color: #d2dfef;
    font-size: 0.84rem;
  }
  .author-line strong {
    color: #edf6ff;
    font-weight: 720;
  }
  .author-line a {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.22rem 0.52rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
    color: #d6f6ff;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .author-line a:hover {
    border-color: rgba(85,205,233,0.5);
    background: rgba(85,205,233,0.12);
  }
  .lead {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: #e0ebf7;
    font-size: clamp(0.98rem, 1.22vw, 1.08rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .quick-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.42rem;
    margin-top: 0.78rem;
  }
  .quick-links a {
    min-height: 1.88rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.072), rgba(255,255,255,0.04));
    color: #ecfbff;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 720;
    line-height: 1.12;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05), 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }
  .quick-links a:hover {
    border-color: rgba(85,205,233,0.58);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(85,205,233,0.15), rgba(85,205,233,0.08));
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .hero-visual {
    width: min(100%, 440px);
    justify-self: end;
  }
  .hero-visual svg {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }
  .sections-overview {
    margin-top: 1.1rem;
  }
  .section-kicker {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    color: #9ee9f7;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .sections-overview h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.72rem;
    color: #f8fafc;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 1.7vw, 1.55rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .editorial-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }
  .sections-overview :global(.card) {
    min-height: 9.2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .sections-overview :global(.card h3) {
    margin: 0 0 0.36rem;
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .sections-overview :global(.card p) {
    display: -webkit-box;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.42;
  }
  .sections-overview :global(.card a) {
    margin-top: auto;
    color: #d6f6ff;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 760;
    text-decoration: none;
    width: fit-content;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.22rem 0.52rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
  }
  .sections-overview :global(.card a:hover) {
    border-color: rgba(85,205,233,0.5);
    background: rgba(85,205,233,0.12);
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .quick-links { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .editorial-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .quick-links,
    .editorial-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .quick-links a { min-height: 2.15rem; }
  }
</style>
